      "created_at": "2022-04-04T18:48:19.432Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/6/6/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a\" title=\"teatr\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/6/6/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a_2_800x566.jpeg\" alt=\"teatr\" data-base62-sha1=\"eEst5Wg08CP6BsaewdbB88JjKf8\" width=\"800\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/6/6/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a_2_800x566.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/6/6/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/6/6/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/6/6/66b1414e43d112ae3dd06963b3169b01892dc91a_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">teatr</span><span class=\"informations\">845×598 122 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 121893,
      "post_number": 12,
      "username": "Albano-id",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/albano-id/{size}/14620_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-04-04T20:42:56.743Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Fundin E te dytit, apo gjithe filmit ne njefare menyre. Ngjyrat e filmit evoluojne ne fund.<br>\nMe beri pershtypje gjithashtu natyralizmi i disa skenave me biseda, ndryshe nga linja tjeter e filmit, me artistike.<br>\nPmvsh ritmit te ngadalte eshte nje film qe te perfshin e fillon e behet universal, ndoshta nga tema autoriale qe trajton.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 10,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 121894,
      "post_number": 13,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-04-05T07:27:34.911Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Albano-id\" data-post=\"12\" data-topic=\"5816\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/albano-id/48/14620_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Albano-id:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fundin E te dytit, apo gjithe filmit ne njefare menyre</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Meqe, me sa kam kuptu, tek filmi i dyte behet fjale per nje xhirim filmi: po me kujtoka skenen mbyllese (ose më sakte, para-mbyllese) të “Drive my car” (pjesen teatrale).</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/7/0/7064604d8505af74aca7f738ec00b2425fddeb16.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"g2gwXJU5EKIW2X8v4tlQ3rGcqNM\" width=\"750\" height=\"410\"></p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Albano-id\" data-post=\"12\" data-topic=\"5816\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/albano-id/48/14620_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Albano-id:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Pmvsh ritmit te ngadalte eshte nje film qe te perfshin</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Une them keshtu: qe nga momenti qe nuk behet fjale per formalizem (dakort, sekush pastaj ka kutin e vet per te matur formalizmin), “ngadalesia” <strong>nuk eshte më</strong> problem, qe nga momenti qe filmi prodhon kohë  filmike. Dakort, kohe filmike, por <strong>kohë</strong>, gjithsesi.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 12,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 121895,
      "post_number": 14,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-04-05T07:39:55.603Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Dhe, ne fakt, kur flas per montazh, duhet thene se kam para sysh, para se gjithash figuren stilistike më te arrirë ne film, e qe eshte ajo qe quhet <strong>elips</strong>: kisha kohe pa parë nje film me elipse më te arrira sa ky !</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox wikipedia\" data-onebox-src=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellipsis_(narrative_device)\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellipsis_(narrative_device)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">en.wikipedia.org</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellipsis_(narrative_device)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Ellipsis (narrative device)</a></h3>\n\n<p>Ellipsis is the narrative device of omitting a portion of the sequence of events, allowing the reader to fill in the narrative gaps. Aside from its literary use, the ellipsis has a counterpart in film production. It is there to suggest an action by simply showing what happens before and after what is observed. The vast majority of films use ellipses to clear actions that add nothing to the narrative. Beyond these \"convenience\" ellipses, ellipses are also used to advance the story.\n An ellipsis in...</p>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 121896,
